game.name: Baby Sisters Dress Up
game.description:
Two most popular frozen sisters Anna and Elsa are invited by her friends for the royal ball tonight. They have arranged all the items except the selection of their final dresses. These princesses have heard a lot about your fashion abilities, so they have now approached you for the instant help. Do you dress them up with the perfect outfits? Join Baby Sisters Dress Up game to help the princesses to look awesome in the party! Choose from multiple outfits and accessories to create a nice outfit!
They are very crazy for the event and do want to compromise their looks. There are countless colorful clothes, hair styles and hair accessories as well as a pair of matching shoes to choose from. Give them a right hairstyle, a pair of right shoes, and a pink frock with some purple work on the upper part, or an orange dress or a green color long outfit! Complete her look with a pair of blue sparkling earrings and necklace and a red or golden crown!
Practice the same fashion skills with the other princess to make her look fabulous in this html5 princess dress up game! Once you are done, click the Show button to see the final result! Try to mix and match as many items as you can until the awesome result will be on the floor! We have many more popular girls dress-up games that are free to play online, no download required on atmegame.com. Good luck to explore the wider world of girls games in the virtual environment!!
